        "content_1": "Morito Chocolates is a Brooklyn-based, female-founded brand crafting cacao-driven confections with a focus on clarity, balance, and intention.",
        "content_2": "<p>We began with chocolate sticks — a simple expression of vegan chocolate made with organic, gluten-free ingredients and a short, thoughtful ingredient list.</p><p>As Morito evolved, so did the format.</p><p>Today, our cups carry that same foundation forward, reimagined through layered textures and refined flavor pairings. Each piece is built from cacao outward — designed to feel light, creamy, and clean, while remaining deeply expressive.</p>"
