          "type": "image-text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Hacienda_copy_abecc716-b39b-4f89-9ace-a04a79cfc6e5.jpg",
            "content": "<p>The Dominican Republic — our home base of inspiration and a land with deep cacao roots — is where our story begins.</p><p>The Caribbean is at the heart of our sourcing — a region with lasting influence on our work.</p><p>We source our ingredients through a combination of direct relationships and trusted partners. Our cacao is selected in the form of cacao paste, allowing us to focus on formulation and flavor development in our Brooklyn kitchen.</p><p>We partner with Hacienda Jeanmarie in Puerto Rico, the island’s first registered cacao hacienda, founded by Juan Echevarría — supporting the restoration of cacao cultivation and a new generation of growers.</p><p>At Morito Chocolates, handcrafted is not a claim — it is a practice we return to with every batch.</p><p></p>"
